      <title><![CDATA[Crysis Remastered Trilogy out now on Steam!]]></title>
      <link>https://www.cryengine.com/news/view/crysis-remastered-trilogy-out-now-on-steam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[But can it play Crysis Remastered Trilogy? Head to steam and pick up the all-in-one bundle of three iconic Crysis games to find out.]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><p>Suit up and put your PC hardware to the test as Crysis Remastered Trilogy launches today on Steam! Powered by CRYENGINE, Crysis Remastered Trilogy features the single-player remasters of Crysis, Crysis 2, and Crysis 3. Each legendary game in this all-in-one collection has been optimized and enhanced for today's hardware to play better and faster than ever before.</p><p>The great value bundle includes ray tracing, high-definition textures for crystal clear images, and visually enhanced weapons, characters, and environments to immerse you completely in the Crysis universes. Improved lighting makes the game look better than ever, and of course, there are substantial performance games. For instance, the original games played at an average of 720p resolution and up to 30 FPS. The remasters for PC play between 1080p and 4K at up to 60 FPS for beautiful, lightning-fast gameplay. You can lock in your frame rate or push your rig to its limits and play on max settings.</p><p><strong>Crysis Remastered Trilogy includes:</strong></p><p><strong>Crysis Remastered:</strong></p><figure class="image"><img src="../conv.cryengine.com/fO8jdBf0NMCINfOGIs9ocRZ-Qy95WB3kaSkJUEQo7SE/el_1/czM6Ly9jcnllbmdpbmUtY29udGVudC9maWxlcy9uZX/dzLzkwNzA2ODMzNWRiYjViNjk3YTEyYTc0ZWFhYzRi/MDk5MGFjOTBhODlhNzAyYTRkNThlY2EzYWZ/QwMTkuanBn.b5.delaye" srcset="https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/768/907068335dbb5b697a12a74eaac4b0990ac90a89a702a4d58eca3afa70f3d019.jpg 768w, https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/968/907068335dbb5b697a12a74eaac4b0990ac90a89a702a4d58eca3afa70f3d019.jpg 968w, https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/1280/907068335dbb5b697a12a74eaac4b0990ac90a89a702a4d58eca3afa70f3d019.jpg 1280w" alt="907068335dbb5b697a12a74eaac4b0990ac90a89a702a4d58eca3afa70f3d019.jpg" /></figure><p>A simple rescue mission turns into an all-out war as alien invaders swarm over the Lingshan Islands. Playing as super-soldier Prophet, you are armed with a powerful Nanosuit equipped with Speed, Strength, Armor, and Cloaking abilities. Use a vast arsenal of modular weaponry and adapt your tactics and gear to dominate enemies in an enormous sandbox world.</p><p><strong>Crysis 2 Remastered:</strong></p><figure class="image"><img src="../conv.cryengine.com/vaMEVM21YK_iWrhNasc61GLWfVQeR_gp3mMK-eVS4RM/el_1/czM6Ly9jcnllbmdpbmUtY29udGVudC9maWxlcy9uZX/dzLzY0MjMwYTU2N2MzMDk4YjBmNTQyOTA0NWVlMzE5/NmZlMGFkZWNkMTdhZTNhZTkxMTJmM2M1ZWJ/VkYzYuanBn.b7.delaye" srcset="https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/768/64230a567c3098b0f5429045ee3196fe0adecd17ae3ae9112f3c5ebb5eb65dc6.jpg 768w, https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/968/64230a567c3098b0f5429045ee3196fe0adecd17ae3ae9112f3c5ebb5eb65dc6.jpg 968w, https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/1280/64230a567c3098b0f5429045ee3196fe0adecd17ae3ae9112f3c5ebb5eb65dc6.jpg 1280w" alt="64230a567c3098b0f5429045ee3196fe0adecd17ae3ae9112f3c5ebb5eb65dc6.jpg" /></figure><p>Aliens have returned to a world ravaged by climate disasters. As the invaders lay waste to New York and begin an assault that threatens the total annihilation of humankind, only you have the technology to lead the fightback. Equipped with the upgraded Nanosuit 2.0, customize your suit and weapons in real-time and unlock powerful abilities in the battle for humanity's survival.</p><p><strong>Crysis 3 Remastered:</strong></p><figure class="image"><img src="../conv.cryengine.com/zUUl5_54gkSbQw7IFD2qoLjD3NVVMIi0CPNP5KJoA3Y/el_1/czM6Ly9jcnllbmdpbmUtY29udGVudC9maWxlcy9uZX/dzLzFhMjlkNmE2OTM4Y2ZmY2YyN2FjYWMzYTdmMjc1/MTVmY2U4YWEwODA3MjU1OTMwOTRiN2U3N2R/JkNzIuanBn.b9.delaye" srcset="https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/768/1a29d6a6938cffcf27acac3a7f27515fce8aa080725593094b7e77dcc2172d72.jpg 768w, https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/968/1a29d6a6938cffcf27acac3a7f27515fce8aa080725593094b7e77dcc2172d72.jpg 968w, https://www.cryengine.com/files/news/1280/1a29d6a6938cffcf27acac3a7f27515fce8aa080725593094b7e77dcc2172d72.jpg 1280w" alt="1a29d6a6938cffcf27acac3a7f27515fce8aa080725593094b7e77dcc2172d72.jpg" /></figure><p>New York City has been transformed into a sprawling urban rainforest sheltered by a giant nanodome. Fight through seven distinct districts against human and alien forces, using the Nanosuit's superior technology to deploy brute force or opt for stealth to achieve your goals. Equipped with a deadly Predator Bow, there's no wrong way to save the world.</p><p>Crysis 2 Remastered and Crysis 3 Remastered will also be made available for individual purchase on Steam. Crysis Remastered Trilogy and the individual remasters are available now for PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5 from the PlayStation Store, Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S from the Microsoft Store, and PC from the Epic Games Store. Head to <a target="_blank" href="https://www.crysis.com/" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener">www.crysis.com</a> to find out more.</p></div>]]></content:encoded>
